27:29.800 --> 27:30.580
Then the frequency.

27:30.840 --> 27:36.820
And then the frequency, and then it was acting as an external forcing term, often all simultaneously.

27:36.820 --> 27:40.520
Which, as we established earlier, is a mathematical nightmare.

